PATH 1

C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin;;%systemroot%\system32

see where it says jdk1.6.0_13? change 13 to what ever update u have
oh and some computers have program files(x86) instead of program files so if your computer does then change Program Files to program files(x86) or sometimes program files(x36)
